  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser requested comprehensive resource collection for AI, robotics, and future energy domains. Manus successfully created an interactive web application at amztgfrl.manus.space featuring dynamic tables, search filters, and visual mindmaps. The application catalogues 45 resources including videos, experts, books, companies, and reference sites across the three domains.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nUser needed a structured way to explore and catalog essential and popular resources across AI, robotics, and future energy domains to enable deeper learning after taking courses in these areas.\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nManus researched and compiled comprehensive resources for each domain, then developed and deployed an interactive web application with dynamic tables, filtering capabilities, and hierarchical mindmap visualization.\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [web_application] Resources Explorer — Interactive web app at amztgfrl.manus.space with dynamic tables, search filters, and visual mindmaps for 45 catalogued resources across AI, robotics, and future energy\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Deployed web application for interactive resource exploration\n- Structured resources into searchable database format\n- Implemented both table and mindmap visualization modes\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Interactive web deployment enabled rich user experience\n- Comprehensive resource categorization across multiple domains\n- Visual mindmap enhanced information hierarchy understanding\nDiscoveries:\n\n- Successfully integrated dynamic search and filtering with visual navigation\n- Effective combination of tabular data with hierarchical mindmap representation\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- User can explore the deployed application\n- Resources are available for ongoing learning and reference\n- Application can be extended with additional domains or categories\n---\nUID: j9Mp4nRE4HWwPfzb9LNPYn | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0147\n"
